{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/Three-js入门7-模型及模型的加载/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Orainsink's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c9e2568f-885c-5c44-b918-2e51bc942cde","excerpt":"3D模型基础知识 3D模型由顶点(vertex)构成,顶点之间通过组成无数三角形,构成复杂的立体模型. 如果要生成复杂的3D模型,智商正常的人应该都不会去选择用webGL自带的api输入点的坐标造图形,存入缓冲区渲染. 正确的做法是:用 3DMAX/maya 生成3D模型,通过 Three.js…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/Three-js%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A87-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%8F%8A%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD/#3d%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86\">3D模型基础知识</a></li>\n</ul>","html":"<h2 id=\"3d模型基础知识\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3d%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86\" aria-label=\"3d模型基础知识 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3D模型基础知识</h2>\n<p>3D模型由顶点(vertex)构成,顶点之间通过组成无数三角形,构成复杂的立体模型.</p>\n<p>如果要生成复杂的3D模型,智商正常的人应该都不会去选择用webGL自带的api输入点的坐标造图形,存入缓冲区渲染.</p>\n<p>正确的做法是:用 3DMAX/maya 生成3D模型,通过 Three.js 的模型加载器加载模型.</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>未完待续</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Three.js入门7-模型及模型的加载","date":"2019/03/09","description":null,"tags":["前端","three"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Three-js入门7-模型及模型的加载/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/ES6异步编程-async和await/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ES6异步编程-async和await"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/跨浏览器开发/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"移动端开发-踩坑"}}}}}